<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mike Lude, longtime University of Washington athletic director, will retire on 
Jan. 15 but will remain at the school through Dec. 31, 1991, in another 
capacity, the university announced. 
</P>
<P>
The announcement came on the same day the Seattle Times and the Seattle 
Post-Intelligencer reported that Lude was asked to resign at the end of the 
academic year but wanted to remain as athletic director for another school 
year. 
</P>
</TEXT>
