</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102590-0109 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 297581 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 25, 1990, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
