ADULT DAY-CARE CENTER OKD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The City Council on Tuesday granted permission for an adult day-care center for 
the developmentally disabled to operate at 1614-1616 S. Grand Ave. 
</P>
