STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- NICARAGUA; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- 
NICARAGUA; CENTRAL INTELLIGENCE AGENCY; CLASSIFIED INFORMATION; WALSH, LAWRENCE 
E; INDEPENDENT COUNSELS; CASTILLO, TOMAS 
</P>
