<P>
"The Crimson Pirate" (1952), directed by Robert Siodmak. 104 minutes. No 
rating. 
</P>
<P>
A spoof of those Errol Flynn pirate movies. The pirates say "Arrrgh!" a lot and 
get their peg-legs stuck in the grills over the hatches. And this time it's 
Burt Lancaster who gets to be gallant as hell. M.F. 
