upscale watering hole with lots of room to stretch out and a hassle-free 
environment. It attracts a somewhat cosmopolitan clientele, but if your idea of 
a bar is to jockey for room along with lots of vivacious, talkative people, 
well . . . have you thought of moving to Chicago? CATHY CURTIS 
