<DATE>
<P>
October 25, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
PETER FALK 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
