<HEADLINE>
<P>
WESTSIDE DIGEST: WEST HOLLYWOOD; 
</P>
<P>
TOWN HALL MEETING PLANNED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The city's Housing and Economic Development Division will sponsor a town hall 
meeting at 6:30 p.m. Nov. 14 in Fiesta Hall at Plummer Park, 7377 Santa Monica 
Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
The meeting will focus on a variety of issues, including housing and home 
services, residential public safety concerns, and code enforcement. For more 
information, call (213) 854-7475. 
</P>
</TEXT>
